leave adultrizal
join "Maximo Viola" right
"Maximo Viola": Truth is worth the risk. I will help pay for the printing.
leave "Maximo Viola"
join adultrizal left
Rizal: Thank you, my friend. This book must reach the world.
leave adultrizal
join "Maximo Viola" right
